nt charles is also responsible for leading and developing mscs strategic it roadmap previously charles was the director of clinical technology at mount sinai medical center from  to  rising to vice president and chief information officer of nyu health system in  prior to  he held various positions of increasing responsibility at jp morgan in the united states and europe and at grumman aerospace corp where he designed and tested software for the fd tomcat aircraft charles holds a bachelors degree in mathematics as well as both a bachelors and a masters degree in computer science from hofstra university about msccareer opportunitiesconsent to proceed electronicallycareers privacy policycommunity relationscommunity relations eventscharitable programssponsorship opportunitiestestimonialscustomer testimonialseventsinvestor relationsleadershiplink to mscdirectcommsc locationspress releasesquality assurancesponsorshipssuppliersbarcoding faqsupplier resource center about msc events press releases investor relations community relations career opportunities customer service contact us return policy shipping options website terms of use help  support faqs how to use our site locate sds invoicing  credit get the latest deals and news from msc sign up by submitting your email address you consent to receive electronic communications from msc industrial direct co inc site map  terms and conditions of sale  privacy policy     msc industrial direct co inc all rights reserved charles bonomo  msc industrial direct co inc  zoominfocom charles bonomo msc industrial direct co inc profile  biography  bloomberg feedback charles bonomo senior vpcio msc industrial direct co inc career history senior vpcio msc industrial direct co inc present vpchief information officer msc industrial direct co inc  vpinfrastructure  operations arrow electronics inc  vpchief architect arrow electronics inc  vice president arrow electronics inc  vice president jpmorgan chase  co 99 show more website wwwmscdire