team   view all publications print text size regular medium large charlie bonomo biographycharles bonomo became vice president and chief information officer of msc industrial direct in july  with sales of more than  billion msc industrial is a leading distributor of metalworking maintenance and janitorial supplies headquartered in long island new york the company serves more than  customers in all  states and in  countries worldwide with more than  associates charles is responsible for the company�s it strategy most recently the implementation of a new pim tool to manage the company�s product data he is also serving as the executive sponsor for developing the company�s ecommerce and product data initiatives these strategic initiatives include reengineering the customer�s online and mobile experiences using web  and  guidelines mobile capabilities and insuring that the product data can support the company�s online and offline initiatives prior to joining msc direct charles held the position of vice president of infrastructure and operations at arrow electronics speaking engagementsnaw  executive summit national association of wholesalerdistributors  g street nw suite  washington dc  tel  fax 6 nawnaworg  naw site map charles bonomos phone number email address  spokeo contact us  live please help us narrow down your search all states alabama alaska arizona arkansas california colorado connecticut delaware district of columbia florida georgia hawaii idaho illinois indiana iowa kansas kentucky louisiana maine maryland massachusetts michigan minnesota mississippi missouri montana nebraska nevada new hampshire new jersey new mexico new york north carolina north dakota ohio oklahoma oregon pennsylvania rhode island south carolina south dakota tennessee texas utah vermont virginia washington west virginia wisconsin wyoming im not sure please enter a full name please help us narrow down your search first name please enter first name last name please enter last name people se